summary: Single, dual assassin, archer scout. Some simple spells. CBBE. Nord. Located in Markarth.
descriptionHtml:
[b][center][font=Times New Roman][size=4]
[color=#ff00ff][size=5]Milini[/size][/color][size=5]
[/size]
[color=#c27ba0]The Beauty of Markarth[/color]

Daughter of Kleppa and Frabbi, Milini is the sparkle of the [color=#c27ba0]Silver-Blood Inn[/color] serving drinks and food for extra septims that funded her training, weapons and a nice outfit.

Despite her childish charm, once she turned eighteen years of age, she was free to leave or stay and work at the Inn.

(Remember to take away her default bow and she will use her ebony bow.)


[img width=1096,height=650]data:image/jpeg;base64,[/img]


[youtube]19JgMy_MfvU[/youtube]
[/size][/font][/center]

[color=#d5a6bd][size=4]Required mod:[/size][/color] Teen Voice by Triptherift

Teen Voice is included as an optional file if you do not have it installed. (required)

(Be sure it is active and properly placed in your load order for the .ESM file.)

(I do not claim this work as my own, it is a resource mod that is free to use.)

CBBE with armor (Other outfits shown are only samples. Please do not ask)
Age: 18 Nord Teen
Height: .93, Weight .50
Location: Markarth, Silver-Blood Inn
Single and dual dagger, archer scout. Some simple spells such as candlelight and ward.
Marriage: No
Plenty of supportive perks and spells included.[/b]

Credits: Mikan Eyes, SG Eyeberows, SG HairpackAIO, BBDrac for the armor, Triptherift for the teen voice resource, Caliente's Meshes, Leyenda textures.
